name: MisterCabin
overview:
MisterCabin.com connects cabin owners and property managers with the millions of vacationers seeking unique countryside lodging alternatives. It is the only site in the travel industry focused exclusively on countryside lodging and cabins in particular. The listings on the site feature detailed property descriptions, photos, videos, list of amenities, and availability & rates. MisterCabin is 100% free for all travelers, making it a one-stop destination to easily find and compare countryside properties all over the world.

MisterCabin.com also makes it easy for vacation rental owners and property managers to advertise their properties and manage bookings online. Owners are responsible for updating their property listings, which include property descriptions, list of amenities, photos, pricing and availability information. When travelers find a cabin that best fits their needs and budget, they contact the owner or property manager directly via the email address or phone number provided in the listing. Most properties accept online payments, offering a booking process thatâ€™s easy and convenient.
